<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WORKFOLIO - Showcase Your Talent</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        /* Body and background */
        body {
            background-color: #f7f8fc;
            color: #333;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f3c88, #3498db);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            clip-path: ellipse(100% 70% at 50% 30%);
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            background-color: #1f3c88;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #f0b429;
        }

        /* Main content styling */
        .main-content {
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .main-content h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #1f3c88;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .main-content p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .cta-button {
            background-color: #f0b429;
            color: #333;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #d09b27;
        }

        /* Featured Projects */
        .projects {
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: #e9eef8;
        }

        .projects h3 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .project-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 2rem;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .project-card {
            background-color: #fff;
            width: 300px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .project-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .project-card h4 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .project-card p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* Testimonials */
        .testimonials {
            background-color: #f7f8fc;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .testimonials h3 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .testimonial {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 1.5rem auto;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            font-style: italic;
            color: #666;
        }

        .testimonial .author {
            margin-top: 1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* About Us Section */
        .about-content {
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: #e9eef8;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-content h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #1f3c88;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .about-content p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .about-content p:last-of-type {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            header p {
                font-size: 1rem;
                padding: 0 1rem;
            }

            .projects h3, .testimonials h3, .about-content h2 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }

            .project-card {
                width: 280px;
            }

            nav {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
            }

            nav a {
                margin: 0.5rem 1rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            header p {
                font-size: 1rem;
                padding: 0 1rem;
            }

            .main-content h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .main-content p {
                font-size: 1rem;
                padding: 0 1rem;
            }

            .cta-button {
                padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .projects h3, .testimonials h3 {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }

            .project-card {
                width: 250px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }

            header p {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                padding: 0 1rem;
            }

            .about-content h2 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }

            .about-content p {
                font-size: 1rem;
                padding: 0 1rem;
            }

            .cta-button {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            }

            .projects h3, .testimonials h3 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .project-card {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: #1f3c88;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        footer p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #f0b429;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to WORKFOLIO</h1>
        <p>Connect, showcase, and grow with a community of creatives, professionals, and freelancers from all fields.</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/signup">Join Us</a>
        <a href="/login">Login</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <!-- About Us Section -->
    <section class="about-content">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>At WORKFOLIO, we believe in the power of creative collaboration. Whether you're a freelancer, artist, developer, student, or a professional, our platform provides the tools you need to showcase your talent, connect with like-minded individuals, and grow your career.</p>
        <p>Our goal is to create a vibrant, supportive community where creativity thrives. Join us today and discover new opportunities, share your projects, and connect with people who can help take your work to the next level!</p>
        <p>Our platform is designed to provide you with a simple, intuitive way to display your work, interact with other users, and build an impressive portfolio that stands out in a competitive digital world.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 WORKFOLIO. All rights reserved. <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="#">Terms of Service</a></p>
    </footer>

</body>

</html>
